  "text": "Find Firefox XPCOM patterns including NS_DECL_ISUPPORTS, QueryInterface, AddRef, Release, and NS_GENERIC_FACTORY_CONSTRUCTOR in toolkit/components/. The core XPCOM macros are defined in xpcom/base/nsISupportsImpl.h (NS_DECL_ISUPPORTS, NS_IMPL_ISUPPORTS) and xpcom/components/ModuleUtils.h (NS_GENERIC_FACTORY_CONSTRUCTOR). A canonical XPCOM component example is nsObserverService in xpcom/ds/ which implements nsIObserverService (defined in nsIObserverService.idl) and is registered via components.conf. Under toolkit/components/, multiple components demonstrate NS_DECL_ISUPPORTS including nsAlertsService, nsFindService, nsNavBookmarks, nsFaviconService, DAPTelemetry, MLUtils, and MozIntlHelper.",
